<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Included species.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="71">
The genus contains four new species, 
<taxonomicName authority="Martinez, 2020" authorityName="Martinez" authorityYear="2020" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Cicadomorphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Cicadomorphus chicharra" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="71" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chicharra">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Cicadomorphus chicharra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. nov., 
<taxonomicName authority="Martinez, 2020" authorityName="Martinez" authorityYear="2020" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Cicadomorphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Cicadomorphus chuya" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="71" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chuya">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Cicadomorphus chuya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. nov., 
<taxonomicName authority="Martinez, 2020" authorityName="Martinez" authorityYear="2020" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Cicadomorphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Cicadomorphus falkasiska" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="71" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="falkasiska">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Cicadomorphus falkasiska</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. nov., and 
<taxonomicName authority="Martinez, 2020" authorityName="Martinez" authorityYear="2020" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Cicadomorphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Cicadomorphus lilianae" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="71" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lilianae">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Cicadomorphus lilianae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. nov., which were placed at first into 
<taxonomicName authority="Martinez, 2020" authorityName="Martinez" authorityYear="2020" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Cicadoforma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Cicadoforma" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="71" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Cicadoforma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
